# Cape Canaveral

|port restaurants|		|police station|			|Kennedy Space Center|

        |	      						               | 
			          |Town hall|

    |							          |
|School| 						      |Beach|

			(possible Coco beach extension)


The game takes place in Cape Canaveral. You spawn in the town hall, and you have to explore town. Then, you find the peacocks at the school, and have to drag them away. You must go to the police station, where they will get you to get some treats for them from the port. 

Coco Beach might be added for more places to go

Variables are: 

Have visited police station
Peacock treat

